name: Cardiac Cloud
description: I took this photo on a Pentax K10D in France on a holiday in the summer of 2018. I'd been hiking the day before and swimming most of the morning that day. So after drying off very quickly in the sun and chilling for an hour or so, I was about to go and play table tennis but noticed the heart shaped cloud and shot this photo. Hope you like it as much as I enjoyed that holiday.
